Add functional test for ceph partitioning scheme

* Add test for ceph partitioning scheme;
* Refactor test_partition, make it DRYer;

Change-Id: I1bb8ef67b93307899424154a42ec438ed9432423
Partially implements: blueprint image-based-provisioning

Add ceph partitioning scheme support for fuel_agent

* Add ability to set GUID for partitions;
* Bare unit tests;
* Backport ceph code from pmanager.py

Partially implements: blueprint image-based-provisioning
